## Subspace.getPnpmCatalogsHash() method

Computes a hash of the PNPM catalog definitions for this subspace. Returns undefined if no catalogs are defined.

**Signature:**

```typescript
getPnpmCatalogsHash(): string | undefined;
```
**Returns:**

string \| undefined
